headline: Citizens Financial Group to Participate at the BancAnalysts Association of Boston Conference
summary: PROVIDENCE, R.I., October 21, 2025--Citizens Financial Group, Inc. (NYSE: CFG) announced today President of Citizens and Head of Consumer, Private Banking and Wealth Brendan Coughlin will participate at the BancAnalysts Association of Boston Conference on Thursday, November 6, 2025 at 12:45 pm ET.
